      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** If the domain is contractible, the function is propositionally constant. *)\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition contr_dom_equiv {A B} (f : A -> B) `{Contr A} : forall x y : A, f x = f y\n  := fun x y => ap f ((contr x)^ @ contr y).",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** Any retract of a contractible type is contractible *)\n"
